 to expire, or just remove it manually\r\n- Next interaction with admin console (e.g. press F5) results in redirect loop\r\n\r\n### Expected result\r\nUser is served with login page and asked to re-authenticate.\r\n\r\n### Actual result\r\nRedirect loop. HTTP 302 between /admin/login and /admin. Browser stops the loop automatically. \r\n\r\n### Additional Details / Things I've Tried\r\n - Setting `cookies_lifetime` to `0` appears to make this issue happen consistently and immediately. I had hoped that using Session cookie would have avoided the issue.\r\n- It appears the loop is between `Controller/Backend/BackendBase.php:116` and `Controller\\Backend\\Authentication.php:58 (ish)`. Maybe.\r\n","score":1.0},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bolt/bolt/issues/7317","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bolt/bolt","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bolt/bolt/issues/7317/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bolt/bolt/issues/7317/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bolt/bolt/issues/7317/events","html_url":"https://github.com/bolt/bolt/issues/7317","id":292760442,"number":7317,"title":"[3.4.6] Depublish date not work","user":{"login":"Raxta","id":3474006,"avatar_url":"https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/3474006?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/Raxta","html_url":"https://github.com/Raxta","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Raxta/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Raxta/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Raxta/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Raxta/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Raxta/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Raxta/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Raxta/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Raxta/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Raxta/received_events",